<plot>This story of two teenagers on the edge of change is really the saga of what it means to be deaf in contemporary Australia. It is an exploration of a culture with its own language and history. Ignored, dismissed, secret - it has persisted and grown through centuries and shows us a different way of communicating, of knowing each other, of being human. Bethany, Scott and the school are its custodians. WELCOME 2 MY DEAF WORLD is an insight into their world.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?649988</url></doc>
